code: public void testSerialization() throws IOException {     ApplicationPrivilegeDescriptor[] privileges = randomArray(6, ApplicationPrivilegeDescriptor[]::new, () -> new ApplicationPrivilegeDescriptor(randomAlphaOfLengthBetween(3, 8).toLowerCase(Locale.ROOT), randomAlphaOfLengthBetween(3, 8).toLowerCase(Locale.ROOT), Sets.newHashSet(randomArray(3, String[]::new, () -> randomAlphaOfLength(3).toLowerCase(Locale.ROOT) + "/*")), Collections.emptyMap())).     final GetPrivilegesResponse original = new GetPrivilegesResponse(privileges).     final BytesStreamOutput out = new BytesStreamOutput().     original.writeTo(out).     final GetPrivilegesResponse copy = new GetPrivilegesResponse().     copy.readFrom(out.bytes().streamInput()).     assertThat(copy.privileges(), Matchers.equalTo(original.privileges())). }
